This records three phases:
- `p13a_reconcile_start` / `p13a_reconcile_end`: Measures the time taken to feed any remaining audio samples that were not streamed during the live session. This is the audio reconciliation step.
- `p13b_inflight_wait_start` / `p13b_inflight_wait_end`: Measures the time spent waiting for the streaming engine to finish processing after `engine.finishStreaming()` is called. This includes the final pass computation.

