- The remove button inside `ForEach` calls `requestRemove(entry)` with the original `VocabEntry` reference, so cascade-delete (`pendingDeleteEntry`) still works correctly even when the list is filtered.
- The "Clear All" button should operate on the full `allEntries`, not `filteredEntries`, to avoid silently skipping words not matching the search — this behavior is already correct since `clearAllEntries()` does not reference the filtered list.
