Each `didSet` observer in `TranscriptionSettings` (e.g., on `chunkingEnabled`, `vadSilenceThreshold`, `ctcBoostingMode`) opens with a guard that short-circuits when the new value equals the old one:

```swift
var chunkingEnabled: Bool {
    didSet {
        guard chunkingEnabled != oldValue else { return }
        storage.defaults.set(chunkingEnabled, forKey: SettingsKeys.chunkingEnabled)
        storage.logSettingChange(key: SettingsKeys.chunkingEnabled, value: String(chunkingEnabled))
    }
